  <brief_title>Smoking Reduction or Cessation With Nicotine Replacement Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Smoking Reduction or Cessation With Nicotine Replacement Therapy. A Placebo Controlled Double Blind Trial With Nicotine Gum or Inhaler.</official_title>
